![](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/LafeLabs/trashmagicmedia/main/upcycleroboticsdotcom/images/logo.svg)

Upcycle Robotics LLC teaches people to build and operate fabrication technology from waste streams and off the shelf commodity hardware.  Sponsors support scientists who create technology, publish it to the Public Domain, and train creators who produce products and donate or sell them to their community.  

